name: "Obama's First 100" the book LIMITED
description: Downloadable Amazon Kindle, Nook, iPad & iPhone versions available now for only 99 cents!! "Obamas First 100" is a collection of images originally created as a way to exercise our creativity on a daily basis. For months, we watched closely as the presidential transition unfolded, looking at multiple sources to confirm facts and strip away any insignificant commentary and opinion. Upon completion we looked at our hundred illustrations and asked, now what? The result is this book, created to inform and entertain those who missed the events of some of the most significant days in recent history due to the distractions of life and the monotonous nature of other media sources. We hope that by publishing our images we can help people of all ages catch up on past political news in order to better understand current and future political events. The first hundred copies are limited editions, numbered and stamped with our official seal on the inside cover. Created, Printed and bound in the USA. Shipping charges not included.
